---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us | personalai.cloud" description="PersonalAI is building India's first personal AI platform with persistent memory, privacy-first design, and multilingual support.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-8">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-stone-500">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-stone-900">Home</a></li>
        <li>/</li>
        <li class="text-stone-900 font-medium">About</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 mb-8">We're building the personal AI layer for India — one that remembers, understands, and acts on your behalf.</p>

    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none space-y-6">
      <p class="text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
        PersonalAI.cloud was founded with a simple belief: your AI should know you. Not just in a single session, but across days, months, and years. We're building persistent memory, multi-channel presence, and privacy-first architecture for the next billion users in India.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-10">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#C9A96E] mb-2">8+</div>
          <div class="text-stone-600 text-sm">AI providers supported</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#C9A96E] mb-2">3</div>
          <div class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Channels: WhatsApp, Android, Web</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#C9A96E] mb-2">90+</div>
          <div class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Free tiers available</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
        democratize personal AI for Indians. We believe AI should adapt to your language, your budget, and your privacy preferences — not the other way around.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 mt-10">Who's Building This</h2>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white max-w-sm">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">CodesbyFebin</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-3">Founder & Developer</p>
        <a href="/founder" class="text-sm text-stone-900 underline">View profile</a>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 mt-10">Open Source</h2>
      <p class="text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
        We believe in transparency. Our core stack is open source and available on GitHub. Join our community of contributors building the future of personal AI.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="https://github.com/CodesbyFebin/Personal-Ai-Cloud" class="inline-block bg-stone-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors">Star on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
